Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.59,0:00:06.07,Intro,,0000,0000,0000,,Imperial calendar August 10th, 2010.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.83,0:00:11.17,Intro,,0000,0000,0000,,The Holy Britannian Empire declared war on Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.35,0:00:18.92,Intro,,0000,0000,0000,,Japan, which was unable to mount any resistance against Britannia's newest weapon, the Knightmare Frame,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.44,0:00:25.68,Intro,,0000,0000,0000,,was defeated, and had its freedom, rights, honor and name taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.37,0:00:32.84,Intro,,0000,0000,0000,,Eleven. That number became the new name for the Japanese people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:15.10,Default,Soldier 1,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "Let the Elevens go"?! We still need to retrieve the poison gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.10,0:02:17.63,Default,Soldier 2,0000,0000,0000,,But these are His Majesty Clovis' orders...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:20.32,Default,Soldier 1,0000,0000,0000,,I wish to hear the opinion of General Patre and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:22.39,Default,Soldier 2,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that the generals have abandoned their positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.39,0:02:25.33,Default,Soldier 1,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that the only one in the contact room is His Majesty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.40,0:02:32.35,Default,Clovis,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy, Lelouch. I heard that you had died during the invasion of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.35,0:02:36.57,Default,Clovis,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thank goodness you're alive. How about it? Would you like to go back to the motherland together?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.57,0:02:39.02,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,So you can use me as a tool on the diplomatic scene again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.02,0:02:42.93,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to have forgotten how much we were used as tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.46,0:02:47.44,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... because mother was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:56.06,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Mother was a noble, but her origin was that of a commoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:03:01.24,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,To the other imperial princesses, her existance was probably an eyesore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:04.26,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.71,0:03:07.70,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Going so far as to make it look like a terrorist attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.34,0:03:10.10,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You killed mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:11.01,Default,Clovis,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:12.42,Default,Clovis,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't me!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.64,0:03:14.60,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Then tell me what you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:17.62,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,No one can lie to my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.04,0:03:20.04,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Who was it... the one who killed her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.51,0:03:34.40,Default,Clovis,0000,0000,0000,,2nd Prince Schneizel and 2nd Princess Cornelia. They would know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.25,0:03:36.69,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,They were the masterminds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.98,0:03:41.87,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,So you really don't know that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.04,0:03:49.23,Default,Clovis,0000,0000,0000,,I-It wasn't me! I didn't do it! I didn't make anyone do it either!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.78,0:03:50.97,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.45,0:03:53.44,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:58.68,Default,Clovis,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop it. Even though I'm only your half-brother, I'm still your brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.11,0:04:02.38,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The world cannot be changed with pretty words alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.88,0:04:11.35,Default,Millais,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Lelouch! You were asleep just now, weren't you?! I saw you stop working!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:13.48,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, you don't need to hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.72,0:04:15.90,Default,Leval,0000,0000,0000,,It's punishment for leaving me behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:18.69,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! What were you doing yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:19.52,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.71,0:04:22.86,Default,Millais,0000,0000,0000,,All right, all right, all right! Don't change the subject!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:28.10,Default,Millais,0000,0000,0000,,We need to finish the clubs' budget inspection now, or else we won't have any money to put anywhere, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.39,0:04:29.77,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.09,0:04:34.21,Default,Leval,0000,0000,0000,,The horseback riding club would get totally pissed off. They might just charge in here again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:38.63,Default,Millais,0000,0000,0000,,Rival, you're a member of the student council!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:42.95,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,It would've been better if you had\Nremembered this at least a day earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:45.98,Default,Leval,0000,0000,0000,,The correct answer would be, "remembered it a day later". That way, it would be too late and we'd have to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:47.54,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea, for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:48.97,Default,Millais,0000,0000,0000,,GUTS!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.57,0:04:52.88,Default,Leval,0000,0000,0000,,That "guts" magic again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.88,0:04:56.41,Default,Millais,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it will give you the desire to work hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.41,0:04:58.86,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Cheap magic like that won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:01.54,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,President! I think it's affecting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:03.63,Default,Millais,0000,0000,0000,,Good to see an honest person in the flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:05.81,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just say that I've been well-trained for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.81,0:05:07.54,Default,Millais,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.49,0:05:09.37,Default,Millais,0000,0000,0000,,They're quite splendid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.90,0:05:13.54,Default,Millais,0000,0000,0000,,I checked them out recently in the bathroom of the girls' dorms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.11,0:05:16.58,Default,Millais,0000,0000,0000,,You have good balance on top and bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.77,0:05:17.75,Default,Leval,0000,0000,0000,,Hoho...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:20.42,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you saying?! Pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.61,0:05:25.94,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez! I swear the president is a middle-aged man on the inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.94,0:05:27.95,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, but she just changes the subject!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.95,0:05:30.10,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Millay-chan has always been like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.15,0:05:34.50,Default,Leval,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we got the budget done on time, so it's all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:36.67,Default,Student 1,0000,0000,0000,,They said that it was a poison gas terrorist attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.11,0:05:41.27,Default,Student 2,0000,0000,0000,,That's scary, isn't it? Shinjuku isn't even 30 minutes away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:44.43,Default,Female Student,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it! There was smoke rising from the Shinjuku area!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.00,0:05:46.77,Default,Female Student,0000,0000,0000,,So that was poison gas...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.77,0:05:48.98,Default,Leval,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything else about Shinjuku?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:50.12,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Shinjuku?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:55.03,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I called you yesterday. I heard about it from a friend while all of that was going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.03,0:05:58.33,Default,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Pictures of the Elevens' corpses are being shown!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.63,0:05:58.79,Default,Female Student,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't bring those up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.36,0:06:02.65,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange. Why are they hiding "that" information?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:20.27,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,To hide Clovis' death... is it to keep confusion from spreading?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.75,0:06:24.67,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,However, if they were to do that... then when they announce it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:29.91,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. My nerves are still too weak for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:36.41,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,The things that the civil officers do are half-hearted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:38.18,Default,Viletta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking about General Patre?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.49,0:06:43.76,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit passed through that much security, twice. With a formal inspection like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:49.45,Default,Viletta,0000,0000,0000,,Jeremiah, you're being narrowminded. Without Prince Clovis at this time, we, the purists...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:53.43,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,I will give out orders. Wait until everything is sorted out on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:57.26,Default,Sophia,0000,0000,0000,,Karen! It's been a while! Is your body okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.26,0:07:00.86,Default,Female student,0000,0000,0000,,Sophia-chan was worried. Are you okay now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.86,0:07:03.45,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I can't push myself too hard though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.83,0:07:08.61,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so that's what was bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.73,0:07:12.14,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,If I miss too much school, I won't be able to keep up with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.14,0:07:16.20,Default,Leval,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch-kun, what are you looking at? Perhaps you have a crush on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.88,0:07:18.36,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I just think that it's unusual to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:21.53,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,She hasn't been at school since the opening ceremony, has she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:23.92,Default,Leval,0000,0000,0000,,Karen Stadtfeld.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.18,0:07:30.20,Default,Leval,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that her body is kind of weak. She only showed up occasionally last year too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:33.48,Default,Leval,0000,0000,0000,,But her grades are top-notch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:38.85,Default,Leval,0000,0000,0000,,She's the daughter of the Stadtfeld family, so she has money and a quiet personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.22,0:07:41.04,Default,Leval,0000,0000,0000,,You've got refined taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.04,0:07:41.73,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:43.62,Default,Leval,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:46.52,Default,Leval,0000,0000,0000,,I do think that she's a little sheltered though...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:50.75,Default,Female Student,0000,0000,0000,,A bee! A bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.35,0:07:53.24,Default,Female Student,0000,0000,0000,,Karen-san, run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:07:58.63,Default,Female Student,0000,0000,0000,,Quick, run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:03.98,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,A bee in a place like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.72,0:08:07.83,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if there's a bee's nest around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:15.26,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, this pisses me off! I shouldn't have chosen such a weak persona to fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.83,0:08:20.52,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, I was seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:23.31,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, she's the girl from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.53,0:08:25.73,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is there something you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:28.17,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Answer my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.44,0:08:35.07,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.71,0:08:38.64,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You were piloting a Glasgow in Shinjuku yesterday, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:39.19,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:40.88,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you a terrorist?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.49,0:08:46.00,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm Japanese, even though half of my blood is Britannian.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:47.51,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,A half?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.45,0:08:50.17,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,But, why go that far?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.46,0:08:59.05,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Um, was there something that you wished to ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:01.08,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:04.03,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah. Just in case...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.68,0:09:07.49,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Say nothing about Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:10.50,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean "about Shinjuku"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.04,0:09:12.58,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you say something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.22,0:09:14.27,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.67,0:09:16.94,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,I will after you answer my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.27,0:09:20.24,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't work? What is this supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:26.23,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Lulu! Karen-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:31.34,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the science lab next! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.56,0:09:34.12,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! I need to get the equipment out for the experiment!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:36.58,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I screwed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.28,0:09:38.05,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.54,0:09:43.20,Default,Sayako,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do? He may be late again tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:47.13,Default,Nanali,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait. He said that he wanted to eat dinner together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.62,0:09:50.33,Default,Sayako,0000,0000,0000,,Here, it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:09:59.32,Default,Nanali,0000,0000,0000,,A bird?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:01.23,Default,Sayako,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It's a crane.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.23,0:10:04.24,Default,Nanali,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing. Japanese people are really skillful, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.97,0:10:08.15,Default,Sayako,0000,0000,0000,,Nanali-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:12.33,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.74,0:10:14.70,Default,Nanali,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.70,0:10:16.26,Default,Sayako,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:19.33,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back, Nanali, Sayako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:27.45,Default,General {?},0000,0000,0000,,As you know, the plans have all failed. We will shut down this laboratory because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.11,0:10:29.01,Default,Scientist,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.01,0:10:32.36,Default,General,0000,0000,0000,,We have prepared a place in Narita. Everything will be transferred over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:38.28,Default,General,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I have no memory of it, the fact that the other generals and I abandoned Prince Clovis is a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:42.33,Default,General,0000,0000,0000,,I will most likely be sent back to the motherland and will take the responsibility for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.86,0:10:47.83,Default,General,0000,0000,0000,,If the fact that I was conducting this experiment in secret becomes known on top of all of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.30,0:10:51.35,Default,Scientist,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. We will prepare as quickly as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.49,0:10:57.69,Default,Nanali,0000,0000,0000,,Just now, Sayako-san was teaching me origami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:11:02.86,Default,Nanali,0000,0000,0000,,She said that if you fold a piece of paper numerous times, you can turn it into things like birds and ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.57,0:11:10.06,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you don't need to talk so quickly. I won't be going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.36,0:11:12.23,Default,Nanali,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:13.87,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.62,0:11:15.59,Default,Nanali,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.50,0:11:19.65,Default,Nanali,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, last night you were a little scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:23.36,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I'm sorry. I just had something on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.65,0:11:29.46,Default,Nanali,0000,0000,0000,,They say that if you fold a thousand of these, your wishes will be granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:32.21,Default,Nanali,0000,0000,0000,,If there's anything that brother wishes for...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:33.93,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.49,0:11:36.45,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Nanali? Is there something that you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.50,0:11:41.22,Default,Nanali,0000,0000,0000,,I wish for a kind world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:45.01,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,By the time you can see with your eyes, the world might be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:46.32,Default,Nanali,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:47.67,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I promise you that it will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.09,0:11:49.85,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.53,0:11:53.40,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,For us, there will be restrictions on our future.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.14,0:11:58.99,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we're protected here, we don't know how long the Ashford family can back us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:03.63,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,If our identities were revealed, Shirley and Rival would be separated from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:07.80,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Our fate is to be tools of the government, or to be used in some plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:13.09,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I must create a world where at least Nanali would be able to live happily.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.27,0:12:19.09,Default,Nanali,0000,0000,0000,,I learned this recently. It's how Japanese people make promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.53,0:12:23.39,Default,Nanali {singing},0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMusicelements\i1}s {\fnMyriad Web Pro Condensed}"If I lie, I will swallow a thousand needles" {\fnMusicelements\i1}s
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:25.18,Default,Nanali {singing},0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMusicelements\i1}s {\fnMyriad Web Pro Condensed}"Cut your finger" {\fnMusicelements\i1}s
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.97,0:12:31.18,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's scary. I would have to swallow a thousand needles.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:34.73,Default,Nanali,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, so you shouldn't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:38.02,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I won't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.28,0:12:40.44,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,At least not to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.18,0:12:56.49,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,This is my only weapon, I need to know how to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:12:57.49,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:01.46,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time for class.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:02.62,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:05.53,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:08.51,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,please tell me what the questions on the test will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.24,0:13:14.31,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,The humiliation of Edinburgh and the battle of the new continent. It's about civil wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.53,0:13:17.48,Default,Lelouch {to self},0000,0000,0000,,So, this power hasn't disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.85,0:13:19.55,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:23.96,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,please tell me what the questions on the test will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:29.76,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Quit joking around and study seriously! You can do it if you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:30.95,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:35.88,Default,Lelouch {to self},0000,0000,0000,,I see, so it won't work on the same person twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.09,0:13:39.40,Default,Terrorist,0000,0000,0000,,How does it feel being back at school after such a long time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:42.77,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Uneasy. Yesterday was a class on History.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.18,0:13:45.38,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wouldn't it be better if I went back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.38,0:13:50.01,Default,Terrorist,0000,0000,0000,,The military's lookouts are being really strict right now. Stay there until things cool down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:52.11,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,But about that voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:53.85,Default,Terrorist,0000,0000,0000,,We can't search for someone with only a voice as a lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.61,0:13:58.44,Default,Terrorist,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, Naoto would also be happier if you stayed a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.35,0:14:02.78,Default,Terrorist,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about Shinjuku for a while. I'll contact you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:06.92,Default,Kellan,0000,0000,0000,,Shinjuku... I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:10.95,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Say nothing about Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.76,0:14:13.87,Default,Kellan,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be... that voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:16.30,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,First, was training for nobles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.30,0:14:20.57,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,After specifying which ones would rule, they focused on those people and trained them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:22.29,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,They would raise excellent rulers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.53,0:14:25.66,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Second, was speed. Elizabeth...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:27.25,Default,Kellan,0000,0000,0000,,They sound similar?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.25,0:14:30.24,Default,Kellan,0000,0000,0000,,No, a memory of a voice isn't that reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.90,0:14:32.15,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Good. That is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:38.04,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,The greatness of Elizabeth I came about from Henry IX's enthronement...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:42.98,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,What I did just informed her of Shinjuku, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:46.11,Default,Kellan,0000,0000,0000,,If he knows my identity...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:47.53,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I must...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:49.45,Default,Kellan,0000,0000,0000,,...settle this as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.94,0:14:54.25,Default,General,0000,0000,0000,,What about the laboratory?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:14:56.14,Default,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,It was moved to Narita last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:57.23,Default,General,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.05,0:15:00.16,Default,General,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.49,0:15:08.40,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Lelouch, later we should-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.40,0:15:10.22,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.47,0:15:12.83,Default,Female student,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.83,0:15:14.81,Default,Female student,0000,0000,0000,,Karen-san, you live at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:16.25,Default,Female student,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have stuff like a curfew?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:17.61,Default,Female student,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.22,0:15:23.31,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Can you come with me for a minute? There's something that I want to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:26.65,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:29.28,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that you would ask me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.30,0:15:36.95,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand our determination?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.65,0:15:38.89,Default,General,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That is why I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:40.39,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,That you don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.93,0:15:43.34,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still spouting such futile excuses?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.09,0:15:46.38,Default,General,0000,0000,0000,,Ask the others who were there! If you need testimonies...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:48.68,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,Caring only for yourself? How disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.04,0:15:52.18,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,I will not allow you to stay by His Majesty's side any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:54.93,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know there was a place like this on campus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:57.63,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's a clubhouse made specifically for the student council to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.08,0:16:00.85,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It was made with enough space so that balls and other events could be held here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.33,0:16:03.30,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,There won't be any interruptions if we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.30,0:16:04.51,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:06.80,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:09.89,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,I found it, I found it! This is what you were looking for, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:12.71,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes that's it! The experiment data.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.71,0:16:14.82,Default,Leval,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, my back hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.52,0:16:16.65,Default,Mallais,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:19.24,Default,Mallais,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done with all of this, so let's begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.43,0:16:20.74,Default,Leval,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:21.78,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of Millay-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.22,0:16:24.96,Default,Millais,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free to praise me all you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.18,0:16:27.57,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Um... what is this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.57,0:16:30.08,Default,Millais,0000,0000,0000,,You knew and brought her here, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.35,0:16:32.25,Default,Millais,0000,0000,0000,,Karen-san, we're going to add you to the student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,0:16:32.71,Default,Millais,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.96,0:16:35.09,Default,Millais,0000,0000,0000,,My grandpa specifically requested it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:35.98,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The board chairman?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:40.25,Default,Millais,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. He said that your body was something to be wary of, so normal club activities would be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.55,0:16:43.94,Default,Millais,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I am Millay, the student council president. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:46.85,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:51.17,Default,Leval,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Rival, the secretary! If you have any questions, feel free to ask me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:54.74,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,I am Shirley! I'm also a part of the swim team. Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:56.91,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm N-Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:16:59.10,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes. Nice to meet you as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:03.57,Default,Nanali,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Shirley-san? I'm sorry, but could you put this on the table?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:05.41,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you Nana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.41,0:17:06.62,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Nanali? You're here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.14,0:17:09.87,Default,Millais,0000,0000,0000,,She's Lelouch's little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.87,0:17:13.13,Default,Nanali,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still in middle school and not really a part of the student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:15.59,Default,Leval,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. She'll be a member soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:16.05,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.62,0:17:19.39,Default,Nanali,0000,0000,0000,,Karen-san, it's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.32,0:17:22.21,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.21,0:17:24.92,Default,Leval,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! How about we start off with a toast?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.58,0:17:26.64,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Champagne!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.64,0:17:28.85,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't that be bad for the student council?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.85,0:17:31.34,Default,Leval,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, don't be so uptight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.34,0:17:33.39,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,We all know that's not allowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.39,0:17:34.43,Default,Nanali,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.43,0:17:35.78,Default,Mallais,0000,0000,0000,,This is for you, Nanali.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.34,0:17:37.86,Default,Leval,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch, pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:39.69,Default,Leval,0000,0000,0000,,Aw jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.34,0:17:42.52,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Lulu, I won't let you have it so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:48.71,Default,Nanali,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:55.08,Default,Millais,0000,0000,0000,,What about spare clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.08,0:17:56.22,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Sayako-san has some.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.55,0:18:04.37,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,This is why Britannia is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.37,0:18:05.25,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:08.32,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's Lelouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.16,0:18:10.72,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I brought you some spare clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.34,0:18:13.70,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,You can come in. I have the curtain drawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.41,0:18:21.37,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry about that. Those guys are too lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:25.79,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. It's not so bad having some mindless entertainment like that from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.05,0:18:27.96,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The spare clothes are mine. Do you mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:29.94,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.61,0:18:33.66,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,You must be pretty fast. You went all the way to the boys' dormitory, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:36.04,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.27,0:18:40.21,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's difficult for my little sister to live in the dorms.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:43.30,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,We got special permission from the board chairman to live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.55,0:18:44.28,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.90,0:18:45.58,Default,Relouch,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:46.43,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.33,0:18:53.51,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Can you get that pouch for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.51,0:18:54.02,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:08.91,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You're stronger than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:10.83,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Were you in Shinjuku that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.14,0:19:12.12,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.12,0:19:13.10,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.70,0:19:15.49,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you say Shinjuku?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.93,0:19:18.31,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something wrong with Shinjuku?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:20.38,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Don't answer a question with a question!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.17,0:19:22.67,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,The answer is yes or no.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:25.05,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear anything other than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.93,0:19:32.87,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't answer it, somebody will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.91,0:19:34.52,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.83,0:19:38.27,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Ashford Academy Student Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.84,0:19:41.99,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm... oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.61,0:19:44.42,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.31,0:19:46.70,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,He said that if you answered, you would know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.65,0:19:57.48,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.99,0:19:59.94,Default,Telephone voice,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like you're okay, Q-1.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:05.45,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,I was wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.11,0:20:08.51,Default,Telephone voice,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow at 1600 hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:12.61,Default,Telephone voice,0000,0000,0000,,come to the ex-Tokyo Tower by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.11,0:20:16.03,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you? The one who gave the order for ceasefire was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:18.40,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't hang up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.59,0:20:22.55,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by, "order for ceasefire"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.58,0:20:25.66,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Your friend seemed a little dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:27.69,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,That was, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.69,0:20:28.50,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Can I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.72,0:20:32.16,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You were talking about a game, right? Some online game or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:37.12,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes! That's right. I'm usually at home right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.73,0:20:42.41,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I told you, you shouldn't say anything about Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.41,0:20:46.88,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,There are people out there who try to show you pictures and videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:50.47,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I can see everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.03,0:20:57.98,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I won't tell anyone. See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.02,0:21:03.28,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.94,0:21:06.85,Default,Voice Recording,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like you're okay, Q-1.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.01,0:21:16.78,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,There's not a whole lot of work to do even though we're the student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:20.58,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,There's some paperwork every once in a while, and the rest is event planning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.87,0:21:23.39,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Events? You mean like the culture festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.39,0:21:28.01,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Things like guys and girls switching places, total silence parties, or holding classes while wearing just swimsuits...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.18,0:21:29.49,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.49,0:21:30.68,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's the president's hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.36,0:21:33.85,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be forced to tag along eventually, so be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.19,0:21:35.75,Default,Nanali,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, bad news!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.90,0:21:38.69,Default,Millais,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Clovis is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.69,0:21:40.06,Default,Leval,0000,0000,0000,,They say that he was killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.43,0:21:44.80,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Prince Clovis was murdered!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:49.82,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}He has become a martyr in the battle against the Elevens while pursuing peace and justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.34,0:21:54.50,Default,Jeremiah,0000,0000,0000,,We must carry on with his ideals while bearing with the sorrow of his passing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.08,0:21:57.58,Default,Female Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,We've just received breaking news.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.35,0:22:01.22,Default,Female Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,The person who was thought to be the primary suspect has been apprehended.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.90,0:22:05.66,Default,Female Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}According to the announcement, it's an honored Britannian.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.97,0:22:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.22,0:22:11.26,Default,Female Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Private Kururugi Suzaku. The suspect is a former Eleven.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.55,0:22:14.86,Default,Female Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The honored Britannian, Kururugi Suzaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.45,0:23:49.70,Preview,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this something to be celebrated?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.70,0:23:55.53,Preview,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku is alive, but why... Why has he been arrested in my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.03,0:23:57.98,Preview,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to save him, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.62,0:24:01.83,Preview,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I have to rush the plan, I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.14,0:24:04.32,Preview,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it, because I have the power to.
